'''詩麗黛瑋'''（{{lang-ta|'''ஸ்ரீதேவி'''}}，{{lang-en|'''Sridevi'''}}；婚後全名叫'''詩麗黛瑋·卡浦爾'''（'''Sridevi Kapoor'''），{{bd|1963年|8月13日|2018年|2月24日|catIdx=Sridevi}})，[[印度|印度]]電影女演員，活躍於[[二十世紀|二十世紀]]末期。<ref>[http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/1148960/ “印度國寶級影后Sridevi Kapoor猝逝 終年54歲”] {{Wayback|url=http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/1148960/ |date=20180616154250 }}. 頭條日報. 26-02-2018.</ref>，她曾經4度得到《[[印度電影觀眾獎|印度電影觀眾──最佳女演員獎]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cn.thenews.com.pk/latest/285150-bollywoods-first-female-superstar-sridevi-passes-away |title=宝莱坞的第一位女巨星Sridevi逝世 {{!}} Entertainment {{!}} thenews.com.pk<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2018-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180225084446/http://cn.thenews.com.pk/latest/285150-bollywoods-first-female-superstar-sridevi-passes-away |archive-date=2018-02-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2013年，她獲得印度政府頒發的[[莲花士勋章|莲花士勋章]]（Padma Shri），以表揚她在演藝界的成就<ref>[http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2018/feb/25/remembering-sridevi-50-years-of-living-the-cinematic-dream-1778749.html “Remembering Sridevi: 50 years of living the cinematic dream”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2018/feb/25/remembering-sridevi-50-years-of-living-the-cinematic-dream-1778749.html |date=20210116210143 }}. The New Indian Express. 25.02-2018.</ref>。在她長達四十多年的演藝生涯中，詩麗黛瑋有「宝莱坞第一位女超級巨星」的美譽。<ref>[https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/02/28/sridevi-funeral-thousands-gather-mourn-bollywoods-first-female/ “Sridevi funeral: Thousands gather to mourn Bollywood’s ‘first female superstar’ ”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/02/28/sridevi-funeral-thousands-gather-mourn-bollywoods-first-female/ |date=20210227110357 }}. The Telegraph. 28-02-2018.</ref>

== 個人生涯 ==
===背景===
詩麗岱瑋出生在[[泰米爾納德邦|泰米爾納德邦]]，原名為詩麗·阿瑪·雅格·阿雅潘（Shree Amma Yanger Ayyapan）。她的[[泰米尔人|泰米尔]]父親阿雅潘是一名律師，母親Rajeswari是[[泰盧固人|泰盧固人]]。她亦有一個胞妹Srilatha。<ref>[http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/celebrity/know-all-about-sridevi_7924.html? “Know all about Sridevi”] {{Wayback|url=http://zeenews.india.com/entertainment/celebrity/know-all-about-sridevi_7924.html |date=20181119234202 }}. Zee News. 13-08-2008.</ref>

[[File:Sridevi,_Boney_Kapoor_at_Esha_Deol's_wedding_reception_02.jpg|right]]
傳媒推測她在1985年至1988年同演員[[米特胡恩·查克拉博蒂|米特胡恩·查克拉博蒂]]（Mithun Chakraborty）曾有一段秘密婚姻，但是這段情未能維持長久，因為查克拉博蒂不願意與他的妻子約基塔·巴莉離婚。<ref>[https://www.filmibeat.com/bollywood/features/2015/intimate-details-about-sridevi-mithun-chakraborty-controversial-affair/articlecontent-pf99263-194237.html "Intimate Details About Sridevi, Mithun Chakraborty Controversial Affair"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.filmibeat.com/bollywood/features/2015/intimate-details-about-sridevi-mithun-chakraborty-controversial-affair/articlecontent-pf99263-194237.html |date=20170503160932 }}. Filmibeat. 13-08-2015.</ref> 有一段時間甚至紛紛揚揚地傳她們已經秘密結婚，又有說婚姻是註冊了，但不久被宣佈[[无效婚姻|無效]] [http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0149822/bio] {{Wayback|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0149822/bio |date=20160803120303 }}, [http://www.telegraphindia.com/1050304/asp/etc/story_4440550.asp] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1050304/asp/etc/story_4440550.asp |date=20161213114731 }}, [https://web.archive.org/web/20071211174708/http://ww.smashits.com/index.cfm?Page=Reviews&SubPage=BioFile&ProfileID=61], [http://entertainment.oneindia.in/celebrities/memoirs/sridevi-261106.html] {{Wayback|url=http://entertainment.oneindia.in/celebrities/memoirs/sridevi-261106.html |date=20070927190119 }} 。

詩麗岱瑋最終在1996年6月2日與製片人[[博尼·卡浦爾|博尼·卡浦爾]]宣告結婚。他們育有二名女兒：[[詹維·卡浦爾|詹維·卡浦爾]]（Jhanvi Kapoor）和酷什·卡浦爾（Khushi Kapoor）。博尼是演員[[安尼·卡浦爾|安尼·卡浦爾]]的兄長，安尼和詩麗岱瑋以前在很多電影中合作過。

=== 逝世 ===
2018年2月24日，傳媒報導詩麗黛瑋於[[杜拜|杜拜]]參加姪子婚禮時因[[心搏停止|心搏停止]]而逝世。<ref>[http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/02/reports-bollywood-icon-sridevi-dies-aged-54-180224222210077.html “Reports: Bollywood icon Sridevi dies aged 54”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/02/reports-bollywood-icon-sridevi-dies-aged-54-180224222210077.html |date=20190406193149 }}. Al Jazeera. 25-02-2018.</ref>2月26日，杜拜警方的死因調查報告顯示她死於意外[[遇溺|遇溺]]（accidental drowning）。<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-43196902 “Bollywood star Sridevi Kapoor 'drowned in hotel bath'”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-43196902 |date=20181229174709 }}. BBC. 26-02-2018.</ref>報告亦指出血液中含有酒精的她在[[朱美拉阿聯酋酒店|朱美拉阿聯酋酒店]]房間內的浴缸突然失去知覺後遇溺。<ref>[http://www.gulfnews.com/life-style/celebrity/desi-news/bollywood/traces-of-alcohol-found-in-bollywood-actress-sridevi-s-body-died-of-accidental-drowning-1.2178719 “Traces of alcohol found in Bollywood actress Sridevi’s body, died of accidental drowning”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gulfnews.com/life-style/celebrity/desi-news/bollywood/traces-of-alcohol-found-in-bollywood-actress-sridevi-s-body-died-of-accidental-drowning-1.2178719 |date=20180226140250 }}. Gulf News. 26-02-2018.</ref>她的肺部含有積水。

2月27日，她的丈夫博尼和繼子[[阿葰·卡浦爾|阿葰·卡浦爾]]乘搭富商[[安尼尔·安巴尼|安尼尔·安巴尼]]借出的私人飛機把詩麗黛瑋的遺體從杜拜帶回她在孟買Lokhandwala區的家。<ref>[https://www.timesofindia.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/private-jet-carrying-sridevis-body-lands-at-mumbai/articleshow/63100049.cms “Sridevi returns home for the last time”]. The Times of India. 28-02-2018.</ref>

==== 葬禮 ====
2月28日，詩麗黛瑋的葬禮在孟買以[[国葬|国葬]]規格舉行。[[马哈拉施特拉邦|马哈拉施特拉邦]]政府在她的遺體被火化之前為她舖上印度國旗並鳴槍致意。之後移送遺體到火葬場地的開篷車以詩麗黛瑋最喜歡的白色—白花裝飾。<ref>[https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/sridevi-is-home-final-farewell-funeral-in-mumbai-today-10-points-1817941 “Sridevi Cremated With State Honours, Thousands Pay Last Respects: 10 Points”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/sridevi-is-home-final-farewell-funeral-in-mumbai-today-10-points-1817941 |date=20201109025856 }}. NDTV. 28-02-2018.</ref>其後她的丈夫根據印度教傳統燃點放上她遺體的柴堆。

整個葬禮除了一眾宝莱坞藝人之外，外面亦有大量民眾及粉絲聚集。大批孟買警方亦在場維持秩序。但是因過多民眾聚集在馬路邊，移送遺體到火葬場地的車用了多個小時才能完成7公里的路程。<ref>[https://www.bbc.com/news/amp/world-asia-india-43221924 “Sridevi Kapoor: India crowds say goodbye to Bollywood star”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/amp/world-asia-india-43221924 |date=20180424080157 }}. BBC. 28-02-2018.</ref>

事後，博尼卡浦爾一家及其他家族成員發表聲明感謝民眾的支持及孟買警方的幫助，並希望傳媒能夠讓他們在不受干擾下悼念。

3月3日，博尼及兩個女兒把詩麗黛瑋的骨灰灑在[[拉梅斯瓦拉姆|拉梅斯瓦拉姆]]的海水中。<ref>[https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/boney-kapoor-daughters-jahnvi-and-khushi-immerse-sridevi-s-ashes-in-rameswaram-see-pic/story-w5ogpPmFU9vqlB9cg9I25O.html “Boney Kapoor, daughters Jahnvi and Khushi immerse Sridevi’s ashes in Rameswaram. See pic”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/boney-kapoor-daughters-jahnvi-and-khushi-immerse-sridevi-s-ashes-in-rameswaram-see-pic/story-w5ogpPmFU9vqlB9cg9I25O.html |date=20191101161827 }}. The Hindustan Times. 04-03-2018.</ref>

==== 各方反應 ====
詩麗黛瑋意外離世的消息被報導後，印度總理[[纳伦德拉·莫迪|莫迪]]、總統[[拉姆·纳特·科温德|科温德]]、眾多宝莱坞演员和粉絲均紛紛在[[推特|推特]]等社交媒體上發文悼念。<ref>[https://www.khaleejtimes.com/citytimes/bollywood/president-prime-minister-mourn-veteran-actress-sridevis-demise-- “Indian President, Prime Minister mourn veteran actress Sridevi's demise”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.khaleejtimes.com/citytimes/bollywood/president-prime-minister-mourn-veteran-actress-sridevis-demise-- |date=20181116120339 }}. Khaleej Times. 25-02-2018.</ref>

除此以外，[[第90屆奧斯卡金像獎|第90屆奧斯卡金像獎]]亦在致敬環節（In Memoriam）中向詩麗黛瑋致敬。

